$ PowerShell: the automatic variable $psHome

`$psHome` is an ordinary → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/String[`System.String`] whose value points to the *installation directory* of → Windows/PowerShell.
-
In non-Core PowerShell installations, this value seems to be → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/vn_m[`C:\Windows\System32\WindowsPowerShell\v1.0`].

Files that are found in a PowerShell Version 5.1 this installation directory include
