{ *.format.ps1xml files

  With PowerShell Version 6 and later, → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/psHome/_format_ps1xml[`*.format.ps1xml`] files are not found anymore in the `$psHome` directory
  because the formatting instructions are included in the source code of the objects.

}

sa:

  Other → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic variables]
